::DarkMouse::

She was laying on the bed looking up at the ceiling.  She couldn't thinkas 
to why just looking at this bot made her little spark jump so darn much.  
What was he? Who was he?  Who or what was he to her?  Where they old comrads 
in arms?  Where they old friends?  These thoughts just ran through her mind.

"Blast! Why can't I remember?  Geez, you'd think something was wrong with me 
or something.  I mean, I just got reprogrammed.  I should be just about 
perfect.  So what's wrong with me?"

She stood up and pounded her fist into the wall.

"SLAG!"
